MediaWiki allows us to define custom templates, which can then be included in other wiki pages. When creating a new one, please add an usage example below, and use the "[[Template:Template]]" at the top of the new template.

== Available templates ==
* [[Template:Hc|hc]] ''block code with header (can be used for listing the contents of a file, with the file location on top)''
* [[Template:Infobox|Infobox]] ''on the top right of every device / user interface article''
* [[Template:Note|Note]]
* [[Template:Outdated|Outdated]]

